snippet.title: Ultrawings Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Take to the skies in the first open-world, aerial-themed game designed exclusively for VR!  

Using your Oculus Touch you'll virtually grab the flight stick to perform daring maneuvers in the Sport Plane, adjust your flaps to slow your airspeed in the rocket-powered Glider, and grab your aircraft's tablet in the Ultralight to take that perfect beauty shot!

Ultrawings features multiple aircraft, a variety of interesting locales to visit, and plenty of aerial-themed missions to do!  

Now available on the Oculus Store!
